WILD symbol appears only on reels 2, 3, 4 and 5, on the top row.

The TUMBLE FEATURE means that after every spin, winning combinations are paid and all winning symbols disappear. The remaining symbols fall to the bottom of the screen and the empty positions are replaced with new symbols coming from above. New symbols are of the same size as the inital spin result, before tumbles.
Tumbling will continue until no more winning combinations appear as a result of a tumble.
All wins are added to the player's balance after all the tumbles resulted from a base spin have been played.
This is the SCATTER symbol. It appears on all reels.
During the FREE SPINS FEATURE every tumble increases the win multiplier by 1x. After every tumble the win of that tumble is multiplied by the current win multiplier.
At the beginning of the FREE SPINS ROUND choose one out of 4 options:
Hit 3 Scatter symbols during the FREE SPINS ROUNDS to trigger 5 more free spins. No limits!
Special reels are in play during FREE SPINS feature.
The player has the option to select the bet multiplier. Depending on the selected bet, the game behaves differently. The possible values are:
Bet multiplier 25x - The chance to win FREE SPINS naturally is doubled. More SCATTER symbols are present on the reels.

The FREE SPINS ROUND along with the FREE SPINS options can be instantly triggered from the base game by buying it for 100x current total bet. When the 25x ante bet feature is enabled, the BUY FREE SPINS feature is disabled.
High volatility games pay out less often on average but the chance to hit big wins in a short time span is higher.
Only the highest win is paid per winning combination on the same pay way.
When winning on multiple pay ways, all wins are added to the total win.
Free spins and bonus wins are added to the payline win.
All values are expressed as actual wins in coins.
Malfunction voids all pays and plays.

Kigi smbolite abil loodud vidukombinatsioone loetakse vasakult paremale jrjestikustelt rullikutelt
alustades vasakpoolseimalt.

Kigi smbolite abil loodud vidukombinatsioone loetakse vasakult paremale jrjestikustelt rullikutelt
alustades vasakpoolseimalt.
See on WILD-smbol ja vib asendada kiki smboleid peale
Vite makstakse erineva pikkusega, vasakult paremale moodustuvate vidukombinatsioonide eest.
WILD-smbol esineb ainult rullikute 2, 3, 4 ja 5 lemisel real.

VARINGU VOORUS makstakse prast iga spinni vidud vlja ja vidusmbolid kaovad. lejnud smbolid kukkuvad ekraani phja ja tekkinud thjad kohad tidetakse uute smbolitega. Uued smbolid on sama suurusega nagu esmase spinni lpus, enne varinguid ekraanil olnud smbolid.
Varing jtkub senikaua, kuni varingu tulemusena ei moodustu enam uusi vidukombinatsioone.
Kik vidud lisatakse mngija kontole prast seda, kui phimngule jrgnenud varingud on lbi mngitud.
See on SCATTER-smbol. See esineb kigil rullikutel.
TASUTA SPINNIDE VOORUS suurendab iga varing vidukordistit 1x vrra. Iga varingu jrel korrutatakse vastava varingu vidusumma kehtiva kordistiga.
TASUTA SPINNIDE VOORU alguses pead valima he 4 vimalusest:
Kui keerutad TASUTA SPINNIDE VOORU AJAL vlja 3 Scatter-smbolit, teenid veel 5 tasuta spinni. Piire pole!
TASUTA SPINNIDE voorus on kasutusel erilised rullikud.
Mngija vib valida panuse kordisti. Sltuvalt valitud panusest vib mngu kik erinev olla. Vimalikud vrtused on:
Panuse kordisti 25x - kaks korda suurem vimalus mngu kigus tasuta spinne teenida. Rullikutel on rohkem SCATTER-smboleid.

TASUTA SPINNIDE VOORU koos TASUTA SPINNIDE valikuga saate phimngus koheselt teenida vi 100x phipanuse eest osta. Kui 25x-eelpanuse funktsioon on lubatud, on TASUTA SPINNIDE OSTMISE FUNKTSIOON keelatud.

Suure volatiilsusega mngudes esineb vite harvemini, aga see-eest on neis suurem vimalus tabada
lhikese ajaga suurt vitu
Igal viduliinil makstakse vlja vaid suurim vlja keerutatud vit.
Kui teenid vidu mitmel viduliinil, liidetakse need vidud kokku.
Tasuta spinnide ja boonusringide vit liidetakse viduliinil teenitud vidule.
